---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
const updated = '2025-01';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookies Notice (DRAFT) | SaniSafe Solutions"
  description="DRAFT cookies notice for SaniSafe Solutions."
  noindex
>
  <Section variant="navy" size="tight">
    <p class="eyebrow text-brand-yellow">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-5xl mt-3 text-white">Cookies Notice</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-white/80 max-w-2xl">
      <span class="cro-placeholder">DRAFT — review and confirm cookie list before publication.</span>
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="white">
    <article class="prose-body max-w-prose grid gap-5 text-ink-charcoal">
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-slate">Last updated: {updated}. This page is a DRAFT — it should be reviewed by the data controller before going live.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy">What are cookies?</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small files that a website stores on your device to make it work properly and to give us information about how it is used.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy">What cookies we use</h2>
      <p>
        {/* TODO: confirm cookies actually deployed (analytics, form spam protection) once a tracker is added */}
        At launch, this site uses no analytics or marketing cookies. If we add analytics later (for example
        Plausible or a GDPR-compliant analytics tool), we will list the exact cookies here and update this page
        before they are deployed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy">Form spam protection</h2>
      <p>
        Our contact form uses a hidden honeypot field to filter out automated submissions. It does not set
        cookies. If we later add reCAPTCHA or hCaptcha for spam protection, those services may set cookies and we
        will list them here.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy">Managing cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You can manage or delete cookies through your browser settings. Restricting cookies will not affect the
        core of this site — there are no cookies set at launch.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about cookies or data: <a class="text-brand-navy underline" href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </Section>
</Layout>
